    "Unfortunately, current sign language recognition primarily focuses on gestures, with very little research on collaborative recognition of facial expressions.",
    "In the future, researchers could attempt to incorporate the key aspects of micro-expression recognition into continuous sign language recognition as a supplementary aid.",
    "(3) Try to utilize advanced models and algorithms.",
    "Algorithms and models are updated iteratively and rapidly, so staying current and exploring improved identification methods and models is essential.",
    "At the same time, attention should be given to the conflicting issues of balancing model accuracy and computational load."
